text.tspan: This template follows the Sticker Construcor Spec (https://github.com/terinjokes/StickerConstructorSpec)
Note that the background contains two objects, where one
is larger and thus forming a border around the other one.
They can be filled with the same color if you want to avoid

To export design, hide die-cut shape and mockup layers.
